2007/3/4, Frank Terbeck <ft@bewatermyfriend.org>:

> Bart Schaefer presented a solution for this and compsys in
> zsh-users #8059=B9.

> =B9 <http://www.zsh.org/mla/users/2004/msg01066.html>

Adding

    _force_rehash() {
      (( CURRENT =3D=3D 1 )) && rehash
      return 1=09# Because we didn't really complete anything
   }
    zstyle ':completion:*' completer \
      _oldlist _expand _force_rehash _complete

to my ~/.zshrc, auto-rehash works fine!
I found the same article in <http://zshwiki.org/home/examples/compsys/gener=
al>

Thanks everyone.
--=20
Kazuhiko Uebayashi

